metadata.title: Ore International Old World Dual Lift Storage Bench, 19.5-Inch
features: Features comfortable padding with plush upholstery over sturdy frame
Plush fabric bench adds modern flair to casual seating
Bench measures 48" L x 20.5" W x 19.5"H, Storage bin measures 22.25"L x 18"W x 5.5"H (2)
Durable and sturdy base, No Assembly Required
description: Tailored style, spacious seating and hidden storage make this Ore International HB4528 Old World Dual Lift Storage Bench your new favorite addition. Perfect in the living room or bedroom, this bench has style and smart features galore. It's well-built with a wood composite frame and sturdy safety hinges. The cushioned top are upholstered in a neutral print polyether fabric the top is tufted for style. Both ends of the seat lift to reveal ample open storage below.
